392
00:55:58,380 --> 00:56:01,300
[SPEAKER_00] je li Trump pravi kauboj?

393
00:56:01,300 --> 00:56:10,119
[SPEAKER_01] Pa je, on je Amerikanac i nudi svijet.

394
00:56:10,119 --> 00:56:13,800
[SPEAKER_01] Da, nudi taj crno-bjeli svijet. America first.

395
00:56:13,800 --> 00:56:22,860
